Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Many amusing things wash up on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Plants and sea shells from the\Nsouth. Giant deep-sea fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes even people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even empty ships.
