Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.69,0:02:20.66,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,1000)\be1}Where Sea Meets Man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there's a transport from here to across the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's probably out fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I should just wait 'til lunch then, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my wife under strange circumstances on this shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you wouldn't want to hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was around two and a half years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It stinks like fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you were born so\Nfar out in the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up damn it, what "home"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just beg Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not right that you got fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The shop was already about to go out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They were just looking for an excuse to get rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why does it have to be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They were going to have you follow in their footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They were quite pissed at me for being engaged to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have been told a lot of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt they thought you'd follow me out so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I didn't think you would either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't the eldest daughter. You\Nmust have had some plans too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go home if you want. This\Nisn't the right place for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you getting on, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Michihi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll tell her I'm sorry when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sea snakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting foggy all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No big deal, we can still see the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the coast over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I can't steer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the ship, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Michihi, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. There are snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind them, just come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Michihi! Michihi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow them, quick. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The boat overturned...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We never found any debris of\Nthe boat that my wife was on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps because of the tides in the area, things\Nfrom offshore arrive on the beach all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If my wife's boat tipped over too, some of\Nthe cargo should have shown up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposing she floated offshore, she's probably not alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just can't move on until I find some proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Snakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you've been waiting for two and a half years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,On the bright side,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,whether there's any evidence or not,\Nshe's not alive anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In the off-chance that she survived,\Nshe must be living a new life now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you start worrying about yourself now too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Snakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to trade that in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For that price, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're taking too much of a cut because\Nshe doesn't know the market price.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask for twice as much, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak as if you know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working for a wholesale dealer for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of you middlemen that\Nthe fishermen here are poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This should do it, even with the handling fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd take it all the way to the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then, how's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's as far as I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask for that much from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell everyone else the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I always thought you were a weird guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we got a good deal today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't much, but have it please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you should leave your\Nlodging and come live next to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be great. Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a shark in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Shiro? You sure scared us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Was yesterday the high tide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, the tide's so high.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that man who was here waiting\Nfor his wife... is he gone now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's living with us here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are, but leave him alone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "nothing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been saying weird things,\Nand the tide keeps rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So many strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You still gaze off into the sea sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wonder if you might just wander off into the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just like last time, when the tide rose so high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,About three years ago, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was foggy just like it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't go out to fish until it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard some boats don't come back\Nwhen they go out into the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And then about three years later\Ntheir boats come back empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Empty boats...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't get back to shore even if it did come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it still bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about that story you\Ntold me. I did some research on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,According to that, it should return soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That swarm of snakes you mentioned...\NNo one else saw it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Those must have been Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard of the phrase "a thousand in the sea,\Na thousand in the mountains", haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That a snake living in the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,for a thousand years and in the mountains for a thousand years will become a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This Mushi holds something in common with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not that there's any way to\Nknow how long they've lived for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones that emit a fog-like mist\Nand live in swarms in the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ones that live quietly deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Both look no different from a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the ones in the mountains come down, and the\Nones in the ocean come up to a nearby sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They gather at a single spot on the shore, and a\Nthousand days later, they merge into a single Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So then... that same thing from\Nthe swarm must be back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see anything from outside,\Nyet I could see clearly from inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever wondered why only your\Nwife got consumed by the fog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those who have the desire to return\Nto land can see or return to shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you looked as if you would have had no reason\Nto live even if you did find your wife's remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you'll keep that in mind, I'll go with you to spectate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're prepared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see the shore so well that it's almost bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the body's there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull up next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Michihi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You left me for so many days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been at least three days, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, you said horrible things to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I complained too much also.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't serious though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see your village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see the shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah it's okay, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your home is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mushi are undergoing metamorphosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's a tidal wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The fog's clearing up, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time we got back to shore, the villagers\Nhad already given up on our survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought that we were only gone for two-three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But a month had gone by on shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Time must have been passing at\Nthe Mushi's pace within the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She had to deal with the loneliness for only three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The following day, his wife's boat\Nwashed up on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, such a nice kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner's not around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's pretty.
